freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Allergy season so sinus and chest issue.  Was exposed 7 days ago to a neighbor who tested positive. She had single vaccine shot so her symptoms were minor. It appears from CDC guidance I do not need to be retested or quarantined and can visit fam?

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I have small kidney stones which I am the midst of having treated. Seems more painful after shot. Slight bruising around area of injection.
